</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> für<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> graf <expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                        Lewenstein, <expan>thumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                            <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                        knecht auf <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> recht niht
                                <expan>sich<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er sein
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> nehst bey uns gehabt etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir der sache in sunderheit niht zu
                        schiken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> umb
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir etlich unser
                            <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, die das angeet, für uns besant und
                                <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit in geredt, daz sie
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> selb <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Marie Magdalene.</ab>
</div>
